# tilly

CLI for easily creating Today I Learned posts.


## Installation

```
uv pip install tilly
```

## Usage

```
til hello
```


## Creating plugins


## Development

```
uv venv .venv --python=3.11
source .venv/bin/activate
uv pip install .
```
